70
00:10:37.417 --> 00:10:39.708
Having sex. when?

71
00:10:41.292 --> 00:10:43.542
You forgot. didn't you?

72
00:10:44.292 --> 00:10:49.125
That's why when you're having sex.
don't just keep quiet

73
